title: Make yourself at home, garden-style! The Windsor
posting_body: ['-- The Windsor --', 'Lease today, save $100!', '(ON SELECT UNITS & OAC)', 'Monthly Rent:', '$1895', 'Apartment:', '1 Bedroom | 1 Bathroom', 'Square Footage:', '472 - 585 sq ft', 'The Windsor Apartment community features three different housing options to fit your lifestyle.', 'Our furnished studios offer an open layout with a modern-charm feel and plenty of natural light.', "We also have 1-bedroom apartments, or, if you're looking for a multilevel floor plan, 1-bedroom townhomes.", 'All three styles come with ample storage space, including a walk-in closet.', "With a breezy, relaxing atmosphere throughout the building and grounds, you're sure to find a living space you'll love.", 'Pet Policy:', 'No pets allowed;', 'Check out our beautiful community featuring:', '❖ Assigned Gated Parking', '❖ Close to Freeways', '❖ Laundry Facility', '❖ Outdoor Spa', '❖ Sorry, No Pets', '❖ Sun Deck Area', '❖ Controlled Access Entry', '❖ Friendly, Professional On-Site Management', '❖ Near Sherman Oaks Galleria', '❖ Responsive Maintenance', '❖ Shopping and Dining Nearby', '❖ Social\xa0Area\xa0with\xa0BBQ\xa0Grill', 'Apartment features include:', '❖ Balcony in Select Apartment Homes', '❖ Cable TV Ready', '❖ Ceiling Fan', '❖ Disposal', '❖ Dual-Paned Windows', '❖ Huge Walk-in Closet in Select Apartment Homes', '❖ Mirrored Wardrobe Closet in Select Apartment Homes', '❖ Natural Light', '❖ Refrigerator Available to Rent', '❖ Vertical Blinds', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat - Sun: 11:00 AM - 3:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>/', '15354 Weddington St', 'Sherman Oaks, CA 91411', 'Lease Terms:', '12-Month', 'Managed by Carlo, Inc', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '25237436991244D9']
